{"article_id":"1ntXwiIe9U6DUlD2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Billionaire philanthropist Michael Bloomberg is preparing to spend at least $ 500 million from his own pocket","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"to deny President Donald Trump a second term ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"according to Democratic operatives","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"briefed on his plans .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Bloomberg has not yet announced","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"whether he will run in the Democratic primary .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"If he runs ,","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"he will use that half-billion-dollar stake","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"- roughly $ 175 million more","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"than the Trump campaign spent over the course of the entire 2016 election cycle -","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"to fuel his campaign through the 2020 primary season , with the expectation","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that the sum represents a floor , not a ceiling , on his potential spending .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"If Bloomberg declines to seek the presidency ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"his intention is to run an unprecedented data-heavy campaign","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"designed to operate as a shadow political party for the eventual Democratic nominee .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"\" That ' ll get us through the first few months , \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Kevin Sheekey , a top adviser to the former New York mayor , told","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"when asked about the $ 500 million plan ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"which is just 1 percent of Bloomberg ' s estimated net worth .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"\" Mike spent $ 100 million in his last New York City election .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"And you can do the math","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"as you think more broadly","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"but New York City is 3 percent of the national population , \"","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Sheekey said .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"\" I ' m not suggesting","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"it ' s straight math .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"But I ' m suggesting","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"when Mike Bloomberg is committed to making a difference and seeing something though ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"generally speaking he ' s pretty unabashed in doing so . \"","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Playbook newsletter","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"Sign up today","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"to receive the # 1-rated newsletter in politics","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"By signing up","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"To that end , Bloomberg has assembled a political team","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that , since late November , has been meeting at least once weekly in the Manhattan headquarters of Bloomberg Philanthropies","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"to consider what some aides have called \" Plan A \" and \" Plan B . \"","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Plan A is straightforward :","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Bloomberg runs for president as a Democrat , not as an independent candidate","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"as he had mused privately in the past .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"According to Plan B ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Bloomberg uses all the data","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"- ranging from meticulously researched profiles of voters to polling data on the top issues","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"that move the electorate -","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"and field staff","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"to help the otherwise-outgunned Democratic Party nominee to end Trump ' s presidency .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Bloomberg said Friday at an event in Orlando , Fla. ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"that he ' ll make a decision in \" three more weeks . \"","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"He also made clear","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"that he ' s not waiting on former Vice President Joe Biden ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"who ' s also mulling a bid for president","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"and who ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"Bloomberg advisers acknowledge ,","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"could draw from the same pool of moderate primary voters .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"`` My decision does n't depend on what other people are going to do , ''","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Bloomberg told The Associated Press .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"`` My decision depends on whether or not I think","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"I can make a difference . ''","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Still , the subject of Biden has come up in discussions with those","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"who have discussed Bloomberg ' s options with his team .","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"In those conversations ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Democratic operatives say ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Bloomberg ' s team members have indicated","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"that they ' re polling","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"and conducting focus groups ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"and are familiar with the primary election calendar and the complicated politics","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"of wringing delegates from various states .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"They ' re also under no illusions about the difficulties of a Democratic Party newcomer","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"running as a centrist in a progressive primary .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"But Bloomberg ' s aides are operating under the assumption","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"while the billionaire can ' t buy the nomination ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"hundreds of millions of dollars can put him in contention .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"\" Five hundred million is just an obscene amount of money .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"It ' s crazy , enough","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"to buy up all the TV ad inventory in the seven or eight states","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"that really matter in a primary , \"","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"said a Democratic consultant familiar with the plans","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"who privately shared information from a conversation with a top Bloomberg adviser .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"The consultant said","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"it was unclear what Bloomberg would ultimately decide .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"But the mission would be similar either way .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"\" They ' re going to do the infrastructure and logistical work","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"to fill in the gaps for the state and national parties","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"so that whoever the nominee is","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"would inherit a state-of-the-art , fully functioning infrastructure , \"","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"the consultant said .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"\" It ' s being done with a clear and specific purpose :","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"stopping Donald Trump . \"","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Bloomberg ' s team knows","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"the former mayor would need every penny","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"to make his case to a Democratic electorate","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"that ' s shifting ever-leftward","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"and that ' s increasingly suspicious of billionaires and older white males .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"Progressives also doubt his Democratic bona fides","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"for having backed Republican candidates in the past ,","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"supporting the stop-and-frisk New York City policing policies","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"that disproportionately targeted African-Americans","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"and supporting gas and oil pipelines","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"that leave some Democrats doubting his commitment","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"to fight climate change","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"- despite his commitment of $ 218 million","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"to help cities reduce their carbon footprint","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"while also financing the Sierra Club ' s unprecedented Beyond Coal campaign","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"that has shuttered 282 coal-fired electricity plants .","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"Though raised a Democrat ,","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Bloomberg , 76 , was elected to the first of his three New York mayoral terms as a Republican ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"became an independent in 2007","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"before he left office in 2013","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"and registered last year as a Democrat .","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"if Bloomberg runs ,","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"his polling would likely show","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"there ' s a path for a centrist in a field of progressives ,","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"who presumably would cannibalize the progressive base .","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"Surveys from Bloomberg ' s longtime pollster , Doug Schoen , shows","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"that 80 percent of Democratic primary voters respond positively to Bloomberg ' s biography .","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"\" When people learn about his involvement in climate change activism and gun safety ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"and when they learn","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"that he ' s not just a billionaire","depth":15},{"id":125,"text":"-","depth":15},{"id":126,"text":"but he came from a middle-class background","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"and his dad never earned more than $ 6,000 a year ,","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"and you talk about the work","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"he ' s done on the ground and his philanthropy -","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"Dem primary voters view him favorably , \"","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"said one Democrat familiar with the polling .","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"With a net worth of $ 50 billion , Bloomberg contributed so much last year to charity","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"- $ 767 million -","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"that he was the nation ' s second-biggest philanthropist behind Amazon founder Jeff Bezos .","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"Bloomberg ' s charitable causes also overlap top issues for the Democratic electorate , such as climate change and gun control .","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"His giving provides a ripe area for contrast :","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"the Bloomberg Philanthropies '","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"compared with the Donald J. Trump Foundation .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"Bloomberg ' s charity has given away and pledged at least $ 8.2 billion to actual charities .","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"Trump ' s foundation agreed last year to dissolve amid an investigation from New York ' s attorney general ,","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"who said","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"it was \" functioning as little more than a checkbook","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"to serve Mr. Trump ' s business and political interests","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"[ and engaged in ]","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"a shocking pattern of illegality . \"","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"In a primary , Bloomberg ' s deep pockets would enable an extended run with adequate resources ,","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"said Sheekey , a longtime political adviser .","depth":7},{"id":148,"text":"\" The pressure for most people is two things :","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"the need","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"to raise money","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"and the need","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"to find the best and most-competitive staff , \"","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"\" Obviously , the first is not a problem for Mike","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"since we started this process ,","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"we ' ve put together a core staff","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"that we ' re very happy with","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"that is committed to staying with Mike","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"as long as he wants ,","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"partly because Mike has talked about ,","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"if he doesn ' t run ,","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"going down a separate path","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"and having the kind of impact on a larger scale","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"than he did in the last midterm . \"","depth":13},{"id":166,"text":"Sheekey ,","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"who makes the case for Bloomberg for president better than Bloomberg himself ,","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"runs the weekly data-and-strategy meetings with Howard Wolfson ,","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"who oversaw Bloomberg ' s political operation last year -","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"when the former mayor contributed $ 110 million to 24 Democratic congressional candidates ,","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"21 of whom won .","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"His top adviser at City Hall and the executive director of Bloomberg Philanthropies , Patti Harris , rounds out the inner circle ' s troika .","depth":7},{"id":173,"text":"A data-driven effort like the one","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"the Bloomberg operation envisions ,","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"as first reported by the Atlantic ,","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"hearkens back to the roots of the billionaire ' s wealth .","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"A self-made man , he parlayed a small Wall Street fortune into a mammoth financial data and information services firm","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"that branched out into a fully functioning media empire .","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"Yet Bloomberg has had what appears to be paralysis by analysis .","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"He had planned to announce his decision","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"on whether to run","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"at the beginning of the month .","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"But he needed more time and more numbers","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"to decide by March","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"- a date","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"that ' s still not set in stone .","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"\" The data ,","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"\"","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"Sheekey said ,","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"\" is a little more complicated","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"than what he initially envisioned .","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"And I think","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"he also realized","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"he ' s not under any pressure","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"to decide . \"","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":391,"left":225,"right":390,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":199,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":197,"right":198,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":224,"left":206,"right":223,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":206,"left":200,"right":205,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":205,"left":6,"right":204,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":204,"left":202,"right":203,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":7,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":217,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":208,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"